  "subject": "Remove dependency on cryptography and pyOpenSSL in python-onapsdk",
  "commit_message": "Remove dependency on cryptography and pyOpenSSL in python-onapsdk\n\n- cryptography and pyOpenSSL are not actually used in the project [0]\n- add dependency on opentelemetry-api and decorate distributions method\n  in service.py\n\n[0] and make it necessary to temporarily install a whole lot of build\n    tooling (like rust) during the docker build\n\nIssue-ID: INT-2349\nChange-Id: Ifabb240a376d6dc96d1563e9884b2abc44321ca6\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <fiete.ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
